      "bbox": [
        105.94,
        587.41,
        541.27,
        601.06
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p163_s0077",
      "text": "with an LS_RJT with an LS_RJT Reason Code of Unable to perform command request and an LS_RJT ",
      "bbox": [
        112.74,
        601.99,
        525.82,
        612.04
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p163_s0078",
      "text": "Reason Code Explanation of insufficient resources.",
      "bbox": [
        112.74,
        612.97,
        316.4,
        623.02
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p163_s0079",
      "text": "c",
      "bbox": [
        101.94,
        624.44,
        105.54,
        632.48
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p163_s0080",
      "text": " Any assigned N_Port ID may be individually logged out and disassociated with the Permanent Port Name, ",
      "bbox": [
        105.54,
        622.81,
        536.34,
        636.46
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p163_s0081",
      "text": "including the FLOGI-assigned N_Port ID; Name Server attributes for the N_Port ID are cleared. Other ",
      "bbox": [
        112.74,
        637.39,
        518.24,
        647.44
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p163_s0082",
      "text": "logged-in N_Port IDs continue to be associated with their current Permanent Port Names. See FC-GS-5 for ",
      "bbox": [
        112.74,
        648.38,
        540.84,
        658.42
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 9,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p163_s0083",
      "text": "a definition of Permanent Port name.",
      "bbox": [
        112.74,
        659.42,
        259.16,
        669.46
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 10,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p163_s0084",
      "text": "d",
      "bbox": [
        101.94,
        670.82,
        105.94,
        678.86
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 11,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p163_s0085",
      "text": " Whenever a new N_Port ID is assigned by either FLOGI or FDISC, or logged out, the nameserver database ",
      "bbox": [
        105.94,
        669.19,
        541.23,
        682.84
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 11,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p163_s0086",
      "text": "is updated and the applicable RSCNs are sent.",
      "bbox": [
        112.74,
        683.77,
        299.53,
        693.82
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 12,
      "span_index": 1
    }
